inhalt: the election is over. the results are (mostly) in. time to decide what it all means.​ that’s a particularly popular activity in a year when democrats pulled off something of an upset — their successes going against historical expectations and the popular narrative that suggested republicans were set to sweep the house and senate in the midterms.
